HEADWORD: Boastful
<hw>Boast"ful</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Given to, or full
of, boasting; inclined to boast; vaunting; vainglorious;
self-praising.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Boast"ful*ly</wf>,
<pos>adv.</pos> -- <wf>Boast"ful*ness</wf>,
<pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

